    "description": {
      "value": "<p>After forming the necessary hand signs, you point your hands towards the sky and shoot out a flare of chakra that shines bright 120 feet into the sky, able to be seen and heard for 5 miles. If you have a nature release affinity you can modify the flare with that element for 1 additional chakra. The chosen element will change the color of the flare. If you have more than 1 chakra affinity you can add as many as you have increasing the cost by 1 chakra for each affinity.</p><img src=\"systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Cheat%20Sheet/T7%20Flare.png\" />",
